{
  "name": "Psionics Crush!",
  "type": "spell",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Icons/Genjutsu.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You create the image of yourself that enlarges and attempts to crush your target by stepping on them.</p><p>Select one creature you can see within range, and make a range Genjutsu attack, dealing 5d10 psychic damage. On a successful hit, the target must also make a Wisdom saving throw.</p><p>Success: Affected creature is able to resist this jutsu's secondary effects.</p><p>Failure: Affected creatures falls prone and find it difficult to stand. If they would attempt to stand, they must spend all of their movement.</p><p>Critical Failure: Affected creature falls prone and cannot stand. They remain prone until another creature assists them to help them stand. While prone in this way, their movement speed is 0.</p>",
